{"word":"H7667 - שֶׁבֶר - sheber - sheh'-ber - Affliction","slug":"H7667","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שֶׁבֶר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sheber"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sheh'-ber"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Affliction"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05E8; - sheber  she&#x0302;ber</b> - <i>sheh'-ber, shay'-ber</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7665\">H7665</a>; a <i>fracture</i>, figuratively <i>ruin</i>; specifically a <i>solution</i> (of a dream): - affliction, breach, breaking, broken [-footed, -handed], bruise, crashing, destruction, hurt, interpretation, vexation."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4866\">H4866</a>, <a href=\"#/H4867\">H4867</a>, <a href=\"#/H7665\">H7665</a>, <a href=\"#/H7666\">H7666</a>, <a href=\"#/H7668\">H7668</a>, <a href=\"#/H7669\">H7669</a>, <a href=\"#/H7670\">H7670</a>, <a href=\"#/H7671\">H7671</a>"}]}